text: Love  is the only hopeSo I came to the realization that the idea of love is something that keeps us alive  I went online to this old profile I had on OkCupid and someone sent me a message  It was like I met my mirror image someone who understands everything that I think and feel it s strange because I allowed myself to fantasize about this spark  Of course I came back down to reality  Relationships are not perfect  they re messy and most often than not painful  But for a day I let myself dream of what lofe would be like with someone who has no expectations and who loves you unconditionally  Essentially by allowing the thought of love come into my mind  hope shortly followed suit  Hope is all we have in the end
